Type: Package
Package: microdiluteR
Title: Analysis of Broth Microdilution Assays
Version: 1.0.1
Date: 2024-04-16
Author: Silvia Eckert
Maintainer: Silvia Eckert <seckert-dev@posteo.de>
Description: A framework for analyzing broth microdilution assays in
    various 96-well plate designs, visualizing results, and providing
    descriptive and (simple) inferential statistics.
